query: SELECT a.id, a.name, a.classId FROM assessments a WHERE a.name LIKE '%Algebra%' OR a.name LIKE '%algebra%'; SELECT g.studentId, g.assessmentId, g.score FROM grades g JOIN assessments a ON g.assessmentId = a.id WHERE a.name LIKE '%Algebra%' LIMIT 15;
